sections.heading: Sections; how construed; intent
sections.text: (1) Nothing in sections 71-6901 to 71-6911 shall be construed as creating or recognizing a right to abortion.(2) It is not the intent of sections 71-6901 to 71-6911 to make lawful an abortion that is currently unlawful.SourceLaws 2011, LB690, ยง 14.
